            <title>[LU-19533] FLR-EC: Test FLR state transitions and mirror read/write for EC files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19533</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using EC as a separate mirror, we get FLR state transitions essentially for free, but we still should have some testing to verify they work as expected.&lt;/p&gt;

